Building for development:

git submodule update --init
make
mkdir home
sudo chown root:root home isolate.bin
sudo chmod u+s isolate.bin

Building for deployment (in /opt/septic):

git submodule update --init
echo "install_dir = /opt/septic" > config.local
make
sudo make install
sudo make systemd
# create homefs_dir and chown it to root:root
